description:
Frances Tiafoe and Grigor Dimitrov are scheduled to play each other in a quarterfinal matchup in the US Open Men’s Singles Tournament on September 3, 2024, at 8:30 PM ET.

This market will resolve to “Tiafoe” if Frances Tiafoe wins his match against Grigor Dimitrov in the quarterfinals of the US Open Men’s Singles tournament.

This market will resolve to “Dimitrov” if Grigor Dimitrov wins his match against Frances Tiafoe in the quarterfinals of the US Open Men’s Singles tournament.

If the match ends in a tie, is canceled, or delayed beyond September 10, 2024, this market will resolve to 50-50.

The primary resolution source for this market will be official information from the US Open (ex: https://www.usopen.org/index.html) including live footage, however a consensus of credible reporting may also be used.
